<section class="section prp-h-s3">
  <div class="container">

    <h2 class="prp-h-s3__heading">The Challenge of Hair Loss and Thinning</h2>

    <p class="prp-h-s3__body">Hair loss is a naturally occurring issue that affects millions of people, often striking earlier and more profoundly than expected. For many, it's not just a cosmetic concern, it's an emotional one.</p>

    <div class="prp-h-s3__impact-cols">

      <div class="prp-h-s3__impact-col">
        <h3 class="prp-h-s3__impact-heading">Physical Impact</h3>
        <ul class="prp-h-s3__list">
          <li>Changes in the visible shape of the head and hairline</li>
          <li>Scalp sensitivity and exposure</li>
          <li>Increased risk of sunburn on the scalp</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="prp-h-s3__impact-col">
        <h3 class="prp-h-s3__impact-heading">Emotional Toll</h3>
        <ul class="prp-h-s3__list">
          <li>Frustration from trying treatments that don't deliver</li>
          <li>Decreased confidence and self-esteem</li>
          <li>The effort of concealing or compensating for hair loss</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

    </div>

    <aside class="prp-h-s3__callout">
      <p class="prp-h-s3__callout-label">Did You Know?</p>
      <p class="prp-h-s3__callout-body">For many experiencing hair loss, simply finding the right treatment can be more challenging than the hair loss itself. The market is flooded with products that overpromise and underdeliver. PRP therapy offers a scientifically-backed solution that works with your body, not against it.</p>
    </aside>

  </div>
</section>

